snippet.title: Lancelost
snippet.description: Lancelost Platform puzzle. Try to find the lance. You must explore the world and use the right sorcery.

snippet.title: Monkey Math Balance
snippet.description: Monkey Math Balance Balance the scales

snippet.title: Elemental Balance
snippet.description: Elemental Balance Physics puzzle. Use bombs to get wood buring and metal rusting to complete each level.

snippet.title: Keep The Balance
snippet.description: Keep The Balance Physics puzzle. Make sure to place all of the shapes onto each other without making them fall.

snippet.title: Unicycle Balancer
snippet.description: Unicycle Balancer Balance the Dog on his Unicycle and help him cross all the hurdles.

snippet.title: Perfect Balance
snippet.description: Perfect Balance Physicys puzzle game. Put all figures on the playing field and try to achieve perfect balance.

snippet.title: Perfect Balance 2
snippet.description: Perfect Balance 2 Place all the shapes in perfect balance on the playing field, don't let them fall of the screen.

snippet.title: Imperfect Balance
snippet.description: Imperfect Balance Physics puzzle game. Bring the tower out of balance and remove as much blocks from screen as possible.

snippet.title: Perfect Balance 3
snippet.description: Perfect Balance 3 Physics puzzle game. Try to place all the blocks on the playing field without letting one fall off.

snippet.title: EenieBalance
snippet.description: EenieBalance Keep the red Eenie from falling off the see-saw while other Eenies try to knock you off.
